snippet.title: Happyland Studio's Amberland, Hommeland, Man Shit First Impressions 4K Fragrance Review 2020
snippet.description:
GOOD MORNING FRAGCOMM!!!

Welcome back to another Fragrance Review with your host Russell!!! Today we're going to take a look at and I'll give you my First Impressions on Happyland Studios Amberland, Hommeland, and Man Shit (excuse the language... it's just it's name) in this 4K Fragrance Review in April 2020.

#Happyland
#HappylandStudios
#HappylandStudioFragrances

25% Off Sale until things get better out there.
Code: StaySafe25

Amberland has notes of Bergamot, orange, labdanum, patchouli, sandlewood, vanilla, and amber. It is a rich, luxurious amber fragrance, this one will definitely turn some heads.
#Amberland

Hommeland has notes of Lavender, citrus notes, various wood notes, vetiver, ambergris, and oakmoss. Hommeland pays homage to classic fougeres, this is an assertive and bold gentleman's fragrance for all occasions.
#Hommeland

Man Shit is an exclusive blend for TLTG Reviews. Akin to Hommeland, in that it's a classic masculine fougere, but adds a smokey accord and some dark suede nuances at it's base. Could be summed up as Hommeland Prive, a bold flanker to the already bold Hommeland.
#ManShit
